tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: SELECT TOP(name, 15) As "User Action", SUM(errorCount) AS "Error" FROM useraction where application = "easytravel-ang.lab.dynatrace.org" and errorCount >= 1 GROUP BY name order by sum(errorCount) DESC

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: SELECT SUM(errorCount) AS "Error" FROM useraction where application = "easytravel-ang.lab.dynatrace.org"

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: SELECT DATETIME(starttime, 'HH:mm', '5m'), SUM(errorCount) AS "Error" FROM useraction where application = "easytravel-ang.lab.dynatrace.org" group by DATETIME(starttime, 'HH:mm', '5m')
